Title: 🎬 Maduro's Forces surrounded the journalist of the newspaper El ...
Description: Maduro's Forces surrounded the journalist of the newspaper El Periodiquito, David Marcano, while he was covering the opposition demonstration that was taking place this Saturday in the Bicentennial Plaza of Maracay, in the state of Aragua.Marcano said he was caught in the middle of the filming when they started throwing dispersing bombs and pepper spray. Then the officers took him to a wall and surrounded him.
